<lb n="0595a02" ed="X"/><lb n="0164a09" ed="R124"/><note place="inline">即由切</note>　瞥<note place="inline">匹列切</note>　漉<note place="inline">祿音</note>　覊<note place="inline">居宜切</note>　臀<note place="inline">徒昆切</note>　胝<note place="inline">竹足切</note>　鄂<note place="inline">五各切</note>
