<lb n="0595a04" ed="X"/><lb n="0164a11" ed="R124"/>下莫加切</note>　蚯蚓<note place="inline">上丘音，下戈忍切</note>　罽<note place="inline">居厲切</note>　憤悱<note place="inline">上扶粉切，下孚匪切</note>　抓<note place="inline">側交
